  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A non-randomised, prospective study to assess the effects of beta-blockers on substance P
      levels and the swallowing function. The study is going to be carry out in the
      Gastrointestinal Physiology Laboratory of the Hospital de Mataró (Spain). All participants
      will be actively recruited from a Linked hospital and primary care database. We include two
      groups: the first group (group 1) are participants taking beta-blockers and the second group
      (group 2) are participants not-taking beta-blockers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
