    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        - Patients taking and not taking beta-blockers

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Participants with heat and neck or esophageal cancer

          -  Participants with stroke or neurological disease

          -  Participants with central nervous system disease

          -  Participants with concomitant treatment with Angiotensin converting enzyme inhibitors
             (ACEI), Angiotensin II receptor antagonists (ARA-II), Antipsychotics, Dopamine
             agonists, Capsaicine.

          -  Participants with severe clinical signs of aspiration, including oxygen desaturation
             ≥3%.
      </textblock>
